<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      body {
        background-color: #121212;
        color: #f5f5f5;
        font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
      }

      /* Desktop navbar */
      .navbar-desktop {
        display: none;
      }

      @media (min-width: 769px) {
        .navbar-desktop {
          display: flex;
          justify-content: center;
          align-items: center;
          gap: 30px;
          background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.95);
          padding: 12px 0;
          position: sticky;
          top: 0;
          z-index: 1050;
          box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
        }

        .navbar-desktop a {
          color: #f5f5f5;
          font-size: 1.1rem;
          font-weight: 500;
          text-decoration: none;
          transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .navbar-desktop a:hover {
          color: #ffc107;
        }
      }

      /* Header styles */
      header {
        background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)),
          url("/images/cinematic-bg.jpg") center/cover no-repeat;
        color: #f5f5f5;
        padding: 100px 20px;
        text-align: center;
        box-shadow: inset 0 -10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
      }

      header h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(255, 152, 0, 0.4);
      }

      a {
        color: #ff9800;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      a:hover {
        color: #ffc107;
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      /* Hamburger menu styles */
      .hamburger {
        display: none;
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .hamburger {
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
          justify-content: space-around;
          width: 40px;
          height: 30px;
          background: none;
          border: none;
          cursor: pointer;
          z-index: 1100;
          position: fixed;
          top: 20px;
          right: 20px;
        }

        .hamburger div {
          width: 100%;
          height: 4px;
          background: #ff9800;
          border-radius: 5px;
          transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        nav {
          display: none;
        }

        nav.nav-active {
          display: flex;
        }
      }

      nav {
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.95);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        display: none;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        z-index: 1000;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }

      nav ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
        text-align: center;
      }

      nav ul li {
        margin: 15px 0;
      }

      nav ul li a {
        color: #f5f5f5;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: color 0.3s ease;
      }

      nav ul li a:hover {
        color: #ffc107;
      }

      /* Cards and grid */
      .text-section {
        margin-bottom: 40px;
      }

      .text-section h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .text-section p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
      }

      .image-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 20px;
      }

      .card {
        background: #1a1a1a;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        overflow: hidden;
        text-align: center;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .card img {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #333;
      }

      .card h3 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin: 15px 0 10px;
        color: #f4f4f4;
      }

      .card p {
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #ccc;
        padding: 10px 0;
      }

      .card:hover {
        transform: scale(1.05);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
      }
      .footer {
        background-color: #1c1c1c;
        color: #f5f5f5;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 10px 0;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        border-top: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <!-- Desktop Nav -->
    <%- include('partials/navbar.ejs') %>

    <!-- Header -->
    <header>
      <h1>About Me</h1>
      <p>More about me, outside of academics</p>
    </header>

    <!-- Hamburger Menu for Mobile -->
    <button class="hamburger" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
      <div></div>
      <div></div>
      <div></div>
    </button>

    <!-- Mobile Nav -->
    <%- include('partials/mobile_nav.ejs') %>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="container py-5">
      <div class="text-section">
        <p>
          Outside of school, my hobbies consist of spending time with my family,
          taking videos/pictures with my camera, hiking, traveling, being
          involved with my cohort in Computing Talent Initiative, contributing
          to open-source/building my own projects, weight lifting, listening to
          music, spending time with my friends, and watching movies.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="image-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <img src="/images/Family.jpg" alt="Sergio's Family" />
          <h3>Family</h3>
          <p>
            I was raised in Monterey County, in a small town called Soledad,
            which has a large Hispanic/Latino population. As the child of
            immigrants, I grew up understanding the sacrifices my parents made
            to give me the opportunities they never had.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <img src="/images/Activities.jpg" alt="Sergio holding a camera" />
          <h3>Activities</h3>
          <p>
            Growing up, I never fully understood the importance of being
            involved in my community. With my parents' advice being "get good
            grades to succeed," I concentrated solely on school, work, and
            family.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <img
            src="/images/Music.jpg"
            alt="A picture of headphones laying on some vinyl jackets"
          />
          <h3>Music</h3>
          <p>
            Music has always held a special place in my life, ever since my
            parents introduced me to genres like cumbia, corrido, banda, and
            much more.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <img src="/images/Temple.jpg" alt="A temple in Kyoto, Japan" />
          <h3>Traveling</h3>
          <p>
            Traveling has always been an exciting experience for me. Whether
            itâ€™s exploring new cities, hiking through scenic landscapes, or
            immersing myself in different cultures, each journey has taught me
            something new.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <script>
      const hamburger = document.querySelector(".hamburger");
      const nav = document.querySelector("nav");

      hamburger.addEventListener("click", () => {
        hamburger.classList.toggle("active");
        nav.classList.toggle("nav-active");
      });
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
